        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>January 5th 5624</date>.</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>113 Canal Street 2nd floor</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="Envelope"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revnd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>371 Walnut <sic>street</sic></placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Pa</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>January 5, 1864</date>.</p>
            <p><sic><addressee>Rev. Isaac Lesser</addressee></sic>,
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p>Very honored sir:</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Herewith you will receive $6. Please send me a set<lb/> of
                pentateuchs with English translation, which were printed in
                    <placeName>Ger-<lb/>many</placeName>. I hope you will remember that the $6. was
                the price you set<lb/> for it when you were last here. I shall be very much indebted
                to<lb/> you if you will send me these as early as tomorrow per express,
                be-<lb/>cause the buyer will stay here for only several days.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please enclose a prospectus of the works which you<lb/> are now
                printing for $5. as well as a catalogue of all your works,<lb/> for today there is a
                meeting in my community with regard to organi-<lb/>sing a Sunday school and I may be
                able to dispose of some of your<lb/> things.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">With every respect,</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <placeName>113 Canal Street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>2nd floor</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
